text: Artur Społowicz (born 11 October 1963) is a Polish equestrian. He competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2008 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Poland Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Wrocław
